                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5096" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0739</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8282 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康芝药业关联并购：大股东的仗义驰援还是花式套现？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Related M&amp;A of HONZ Pharmaceutical: Major Shareholder&#39;s Propping or Tunneling?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒲丹琳，李超仪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康芝药业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关联并购；掏空行为；支持行为；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Related M&amp;A; Tunneling; Propping; Corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康芝药业是我国第一家专营儿童用药的上市公司，一度拥有良好的发展势头。2018年7月，康芝药业高溢价并购了处于大股东同一控制下的另一家子公司——中山爱护，称是为其“儿童大健康”战略布局。但经分析发现，大股东的家族人员在并购前高价退出标的投资，中山爱护的高估值、大股东的高业绩承诺存在虚高的成分，上市公司也因这场并购耗光流动资金。这不禁让人质疑大股东此举究竟是为了“支持”还是“掏空”。本案例追溯了康芝药业的发展历程，梳理了并购的方案和过程，回顾了交易各方、投资者和监管方的反应和行动。案例旨在以康芝药业为例，分析大股东主导下关联并购的实施动因及后果，同时探讨与之相关的公司治理和外部监管问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">HONZ Pharmaceutical is the first listed company specializing in children&#39;s medicine in China, which once had a good momentum of development. In July 2018, HONZ Pharmaceutical acquired another subsidiary under the same control of major shareholders at a high premium, Zhongshan Care, claimed as its strategic layout of &quot;children&#39;s health&quot;. However, after analysis, it is found that the family members of the major shareholders withdraw from the target investment at a high price before the merger, the overvalued value cherished by Zhongshan and the high performance commitment of the major shareholders are falsely high, and the listed companies were running out of liquidity due to the merger. It can&#39;t help but question whether the major shareholders&#39; move is &quot; propping &quot; or &quot; tunneling &quot;. This case traces the development process of HONZ Pharmaceutical, combs the plan and process of its related M&amp;A case, and reviews the reactions and actions of all parties involved in the transaction, investors and regulators. The purpose of the case is to take HONZ Pharmaceutical as an example to analyze the causes and consequences of the implementation of related M&amp;A led by major shareholders, and to explore the related issues of corporate governance and external supervision.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务管理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关联并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
